<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>
<body>
	
<p>The following message was posted on <a href="http://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/items/<%= @cdata['item'].id.to_i %>/view?auth_token=<%= @cdata['recipient'].authentication_token %>">InterMix</a> in the '<%= @cdata['group'].name %>' forum, where you are a member:</p>

<hr/>

<div>
<%=raw @message %>
</div>

<hr/>

To respond to <a href="http://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/items/<%= @cdata['item'].id.to_i %>/view?auth_token=<%= @cdata['recipient'].authentication_token %>">this post</a>, log into the <a href="http://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/groups/<%= @cdata['item'].group_id.to_i %>/forum?auth_token=<%= @cdata['recipient'].authentication_token %>">Forum</a>, or simply reply to this message. Please remove quotes and footers from previous messages. For available e-mail commands, send a blank message to <%= @cdata['group'].shortname %>-admin@intermix.cr8.com for an automated answer. If you have problems, write to the moderator at <%= @cdata['group'].shortname %>-owner@intermix.cr8.com. To block emails from the Voices of Humanity social media, <a href="http://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/optout?auth_token=<%= @cdata['recipient'].authentication_token %>">click here</a>.

<hr/>

<% if @cdata and @cdata['logo'].to_s != '' -%>	
<img src="<%= @cdata['logo'] %>"/>
<% else -%>
<img src="http://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/images/logo.gif"/>
<% end -%><br/>
<%= @cdata['group'].name if @cdata['group'] %>

<br/><br/>


<img src="http://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/pixel/<%= @cdata['item'].id.to_i if @cdata['item'] %>_<%= @cdata['recipient'].id.to_i if @cdata['recipient'] %>.gif" width="0" height="0" border="0" style="display:none">

</body>
</html>
